{"4248920": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "破產勇者的冒險", "steam_appid": 4248920, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你曾是傳說中的勇者。<br>如今卻深陷債務，只能接下本不該接的委託。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一名神秘的委託人向你提出條件：<br>只要收集七名在戰爭中死去的戰士之魂，就能清償所有債務。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/60b0bd881337b704dc03449315048d08.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >這些戰士如今化為怨魂，徘徊在危險的地下城中。<br>你使用<strong>魂之容器</strong>，收集靈魂，並窺見他們生前的記憶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/638d61b3a8fc0902b9770656d092c60b.poster.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/638d61b3a8fc0902b9770656d092c60b.webm?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/638d61b3a8fc0902b9770656d092c60b.mp4?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但這不只是一款劇情遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/eee9d6c23540a1a439ab0779b49165ef.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作主打<strong>拖曳式解謎戰鬥</strong>。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拖曳並完成謎題，轉化為<strong>投射物</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >發射投射物攻擊敵人</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解謎與戰鬥自然結合</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/4370d94519d24ade398e56855541f6c1.poster.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/4370d94519d24ade398e56855541f6c1.webm?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/4370d94519d24ade398e56855541f6c1.mp4?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/44d6374391ee56fe8fa2189898f80c05.poster.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1170 height=656 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/44d6374391ee56fe8fa2189898f80c05.webm?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/44d6374391ee56fe8fa2189898f80c05.mp4?t=1773887479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著遊戲進行：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >擊敗敵人獲得資源</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >強化角色能力</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑戰更強大的怨魂與首領</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4248920/extras/e7af10d25547f12b98d388493b0d416a.avif?t=1773887479\" width=1560 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >原本單純的委託，逐漸演變為危險的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成謎題，<br>發射攻擊，<br>揭開靈魂背後的秘密。</p>", "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲介紹</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_para